values:
its pretty sad that that one episode of laguna beach made me cry.
i really hate everything right now
and i don't think i'm going to write in here anymore because it's kind of pointless.
i still am not 100% comfortable just saying what i think in here. friends only, private, or not.  so i guess this will be it.

i just got back from vacation this afternoon and overall it was very relaxing. i had such bad plans going into this vacation but madison was able to talk me out of doing anything stupid. anyway, saturday eugene had his show and a party afterwards. with the state of mind that i was in i thought for a fleeting moment that we would be getting back together, but i came back today to recieve a message on my phone from his new girlfriend to stay away from him. but after all the thinking i did this week, i don't feel that bad. i really, really hope that i am finally over him. this summer hasn't been that good to me. the whole obsession with gabe was ridiculous and stupid. i really can't believe that i could be so dumb. i can't wait for school to start. i need to focus on something else.

honestly, today was one of the most disappointing days ever.  it kind of makes me never want to leave my room again. but if you know of anything that you think will cheer me up, im open to it.  i just feel like i have no energy left at all.  i've basically come to the end of road.  there are no more choices for me and i guess i kind of got used to being able to go back to my default.  but i don't have that anymore, and i didn't realize it would be the worst feeling in the world.  i really do hate myself right now.

 can't say you weren't expecting this.

monday-tuesday: nothing.
wednesday: i got my industrial done & my attitude in check.
thursday: hung out with gabe
today: city with alex, mostly because he wanted to take some pictures.
that's it really.
vaca soon.

geeze
ive been getting  bozzy so much lately, even after i said i would never ever ever again
i am bad at keeping promises, espcially the ones i make to myself.  i havent really slept since thursday.
i am so tired rightnow. i dont know why im wasting time being awake typing this.
i got home at 5 am today and mom hasnt said anythingto me about it, i think i actually am getting away with this kind of behavior again.  theyve just stopped caring i guess. i do what i want fuck u guys.
im gonna go sleepy now.
hi to gabe! :)

i realized today that i haven't been to church in such a long time.  this whole time i've been so worried about something and didn't even think that i could leave it in His hands.  i feel horrible about what i've done and know that He doesn't approve, but at least i feel a little safer now.  i know nothing bad will happen to me.  this is the calmest i've felt in a long time.  and to all of you who say religion is bullshit i don't care.  maybe it is just for people who are weak and need something to believe in, but it'shelped me more than anything else has.

everything sucks right now and i cant wait to get out of here and go on vacation. i hate how i trusted somone so much, enough to call them my best friend and they couldnt even have the decency or kindness to just look out for me. just this ONE time.  honestly i think this is the most selfish thing anyone has ever done to me and i never ever want to speak to you again.  why do i always befriend the shittiest people
i'm going on a date tomorrow night. so wish me luck i am sick of frogs. or at least 1 frog in particular. and this time i'm trying REALLY hard to never see one again. :/

i had a terrible conversation with someone who's very important to me. i dont understand why they always think they should make me feel bad. so the day ended kind of crappy. earlier i had gone over to justin's to watch some movies and SMOKE SOME, but that was it. today was much better in comparison. i brought perry to the park so he could run around and i read for awhile, hung out with this kid gabe. now i think i'm going to go swimming.//im just really upset that i forgive people so easily because a few weeks ago i said never again, and then i forgave him and he has the audacity to just be so mean to me. its like he does it on purpose because he knows how much it hurts me. i'm so sick of being treated this way. you dont tell someone that you love them and then act like that. i dont know what to do. this isnt the first time i've come to this conclusion. this is really hard for me and it'd be nice if some of my friends would help me out instead of always criticizing me.

i am home, finally.  the week was good, but now i'm here, alone and i feel sort of empty.  i hate when i go from being surrounded by people, to being all by myself, it's depressing.
and i miss my boyfriend.
so somebody call me.

i have been swimming the whole entire day and me and shanna banana are so cited to go to the hamptonsssss to see grandma and grandpa!  we're leaving at 10 tonight.  i dunno why so late.  i cant wait to go to the beach.  i hope its sunny and hot everyday.
i guess that's it i have nothing else to say.  eugene is back in 2 weeeeeeeeeeeeks.

so we're going to the hamptons for july 4th, and i think we're going to end up staying a lot longer.  shannon is here til then.  yesterday night we went to the party with greg.  ended up coming home before it was over.  all of the people there were so old, it was weird.  it was way sketchy, i didn't feel comfortable at all.  some guy offered me cocaine.. what's that all about.  i'll admit a teeny tiny part of me wanted to try it but eh, i'm over that stuff for now.  today, took Shannon shopping, then went to the movies with nick and christina.  we saw the new batman and it was better than i expected it to be.  after we went to nick's for ice cream and that was it.  i was so excited to get a call from my boyfriend today.  i'm happy that he's not mad at me anymore.  he makes me sososo happy.  i cannot wait til he's back.

im so sleepy, i barely got any sleep last night. today was much, much better than yesterday. i got my hair done and stuff and then lunch with greg which i think is what i really cheered me up. he invited me to a party tomorrow that he promises will be very classy. maybe it will be good to hang out with a different crowd. it's really bad to be getting drunk at 11am. right down the road to alcoholism. thats pretty sad that i've sunk that low. i'd say no more drinking ever, but thats not a realistic thing to say. whatever. i dont know what to write anymore

today was just one of those days.  sabin, chris, and marco came over to swim and stuff.  i got so wasted and it was just a bad time overall.  who gets drunk at 11 in the morning?  after i woke up later i felt horrible because i'm realizing what kind of person i am..not a good person.  all i do is complain about the way i am and i've done nothing to change it.  i guess i feel if i wasnt doing all these things all the time there would be nothing to me.  i would be doing nothing.  its easier to succumb to these things so i dont have time to think about the things that really depress me.  i layed in the grass today til it was pitch black out.  just thinking about all the things that upset me.  i know eugene said i have to get my shit together but i dont know where to start.  i miss him a lot today because i had no one  i could really talk to about this.  i cant wait for him to get back.

you'd never guess who i kind of miss a teeny tiny bit right now. eep. i hate that . but anyway, this weekend was a lot of  fun.  friday,got my report card.  i failed 2 regents which bummed me out a lot.  then eugene told me he wanted to see me, so i had to drive all the way to the airport to say bye.  eben though he makes me so mad all the time, i still love him.  but this break feels really good.  when he gets back we'll talk again.  after that i went shopping with christina (sale at vicky's!), saturday was justin's graduation and he had a little party after, then later i went to ryan's party which was the best of all.  we got to dance and stuff; justin came with me to that.  i got so drunk and justin had to drive me home and my car was at his house all day.  i didnt wake up til 1230.  today hannah's parents had a barbeque, and she invited some of us girls to liven it up.  more dancing and then  i came home.  watch the andy milonakis show.  its making me laugh.

so im free now and all of a sudden everybody disappears and i have nobody to hang out with! what the fuck im so pissed.  i wanna go to taco bell, but all my money has run out, i guess that's what i get for buying all that weed. i will never smoke again. thats my end of the school year resolution.  or at least for this week til sunday right.  im going with zach saturday night and im excited for that. theres a lot to look forward to this summer.  brett/justin/nick/olivia/sabin/margo/somebody   CALL ME!
im ready...

you know, i was just sitting here looking over the periodic table and i got so sad all of sudden.  like out of nowhere.  and i was just thinking maybe for once if i could be alittle less reserved and try and be myself for once.  it's getting depressing being in this little shell all the time.  the worst part is that i cant even be mean without drinking or being high.  i guess im just scared of what people will really think of me, and i can just use that as an excuse for my behavior.  i'm really sorry to all the people who have tried to talk to me in the past and seems like i just brushed you off.  im really not a mean person, it just takes me SO long to get used to people.  it takes forever for me to make new friends and to open up to people.ust wish i could be a little more content with who i am and more confident.  because i dont feel very good about myself right now.  everyday i say i'm going to be different and just walk up to someone new and say hi, but i cant.  nothing ever goes the way i imagine in my head, and i guess thats the problem.  i spend to much time imagining and planning things instead of just doing it.  and plus it's only be +or- 3 days and i feel lonely already.  how pitiful is that.  that some dumb boy who wasn't even that nice to me, made me feel somewhat complete.  i guess all i want is some affection. once all this testing is over i want to find someone who will just accept me and who i can be myself around so i can stop faking and just get what i want for once.  this is all so tiresome.
he's So So So cute.

uhm hm. i write on here tooooo much.  i dunno im just bored and i should be studying, but i cant.a h this is the worst ive procrastinated ever.  i went over to margo's and smoked with her and and brett and justin and then came home and just stared at a page for awhile and then last night i actually ended up going to a party with alex and his friends.  it was pretty laid back.  for once everyone wasnt getting wasted. and i got see nick and some other people i havent hung out with in awhile.  even eugene was there but i didnt talk to him, i didnt freak out or anything feels so good. i heard that new batman is good, i might go see it itonite. i dunno anything but studying

so it's over... AGAIN.  eugene and i are "taking a break"  because that's what he wants.  my "problems and drama"  are really starting to get to him and he'd rather if i took some time to figure it all out and when he gets back we can "start talking again"  i'm over it though.  i dont think it's worth it anymore.  i say i love him all the time and he constantly leaves me questioning if he loves me. and last night i thought i was to crumble into a million teeny tiny pieces, but now i don't it's not as bad.  i feel optimistic about what's going to happen now.  like every time this has happened  i said i would be okay, and that i would not let eugene trick me into getting back with him.  but this time i truly do feel like i will be okay, but who knows what's going to happen a couple weeks or months from now.  but i dont even have time to think about it.  three regents this week and i just need to study.  i fooled around all year (MOSTLY with him) and now i dont even know anything about any of the subjects. so back to studying.

QUICK RANT BEFORE I ACTUALLY GO STUDY WHICH I'VE BEEN TRYING TO DO ALL DAY, BUT I'VE BEEN SO UNSELFISH WORRYING ABOUT OTHER PEOPLE AND MY EYES ARE TEARING AND I KEEP SNEEZING SO ITS HARD TO CONCENTRATE. AND I TRIED TO DRIVE OVER TO COME SEE YOU AND MAKE SURE YOURE OKAY, BUT MY CAR WONT START EVEN THOUGH ITS ONLY 3 YEARS OLD. AND WHEN I CALLED YOU TO TELL YOU THIS YOU WERENT EVEN HOME, DESPITE THAT YOU HAD TOLD ME YOU COULDNT GO ANYWHERE BECAUSE OF THE SITUATION YOU WERE IN. YOU WERE REALLY SORRY YOU COULDNT SEE ME, BUT I UNDERSTOOD, BECAUSE I AM A COMPASSIONATE AND CARING PERSON. SO WHAT I DONT UNDERSTAND IS IF YOU COULDNT POSSIBLY MAKE IT OUT OF YOUR HOUSE WHERE ARE YOU NOW? AND THIS DOES NOT COUNT AS SMOTHERING YOU OR NOT GIVING YOU SPACE WHY SHOULD I CARE IF YOU DONT I AM SO UPSET RIGHT NOW ITS RIDICULOUS. THANKN YOU FOR RUINING MY DAY. I DONT KNOW WHY I GET SO HUNG UP ON YOU, SPEND ALL MY TIME THINKING ABOUT YOU, CARING SO MUCH ABOUT YOU, WHEN YOU CAN BARELY EVEN RETURN THE FAVOR. IF I AM REALLY AS INSIGNIFICANT AS YOU ALWAYS MAKE ME FEEL, THEN JUST BE HONEST ABOUT IT INSTEAD OF STRINING ME ALONG, PLAYING WITH ME. I'M TIRED OF ALWAYS TRYING TO MAKE YOU HAPPY AND BE PERFECT FOR YOU. YOU HAVE YOUR PROBLEMS AND I ALWAYS TAKE THE TIME TO LISTEN AND LET YOU MAKE EXCUSES FOR YOUR BEHAVIOR. IM DONE WITH THAT.THISISYOURLASTWARNING. I ALWAYS TELL MY SELF THAT IM MAKING A BIG DEAL ABOUT NOTHING AND I SHOULDNT SAY ANYTHING TO YOU, BUT IM SICK OF ALWAYS FEELING SICK. 2 WEEKS OF HAPPINESS ENDING IN ANOTHER 2 WEEKS OF SADDNESS IS NOT RIGHT. I KNOW THINGS CANT BE GOOD ALL THE TIME, BUT ITS AS IF YOU WANT ME TO BE NEEDY SO YOU CAN JUST PUSH ME AWAY. STOP ACTING LIKE I ALWAYS CALL YOU, OR LIKE I ALWAYS AM BEGGING TO BE WITH YOU BECAUSE THATS NOT THE CASE. DONT TELL YOUR FRIENDS LIES ABOUT HOW I NEVER WANT YOU TO SPEND TIME WITH THEM OR THAT I ALWAYS WANT TO TAG ALONG WITH YOU GUYS. IM NOT YOUR LITTLE SISTER. STOP TREATING ME LIKE THIS. I NEVER WANTED TO SAY THIS, BUT YOU DONT REALIZE HOW LUCKY YOU ARE TO HAVE ME BECAUSE NOT ALOT OF PEOPLE WOULD KEEP COMING BACK TO YOU EVERY SINGLE TIME.. SURE IVE MADE SOME MISTAKES ALONG THE WAY, BUT HOW COME IT'S ALWAYS ME THATS UPSET AND NEVER YOU. I CANT EVEN SAY I DONT NEED YOU BECAUSE YOURE THE ONLY PERSON I CAN REALLY TALK TO. I'VE FUCKING PAINTED MYSELF INTO A CORNER.

things have been going downhill somewhat in the past week or so.
friday we had a last day of school party at jake's. not that i remember much.  but eugene was mad at me again because i told him i stopped smoking and i really didnt.  and it's like all week he's been trying to get back at me for that.  he was acting so immature, eric and chuckie called me just to tell me they all went to a strip club.  why, i dont know, i tried to act like i didnt care, but i did.  and now im sick and i feel so bad.  and eugene called me at like 3 oclock this morning because he was in an accident and that made feel so bad that i've been mad at him.  and we actually had a real talk, something we havent done in a really, really long time.  and he told me all the stuff thats been bothing and why he's been so distant.  i guess i feel better about everything now.  i love him so much and he leaves in 9 days.  i'm going to miss him a lot, i'm not sure what i'm going to do not seeing him for a month.
that's all.

i'm actually home today!  i havent slept in my own bed since wednesday i think...  the lsat week has been fun since i have my car back finally.  thursday was eugene.  i went to dinner with him and eric then to his house.  friday night blazed with sabin and the boys then went to a party which i dont remember.  saturday woke up so late then saw eugene at night til morning, uhm sunday nick, dustin, ryan, me and some other people had a bonfire at the lake, then today nothing really.  just homework and catching up on some sleep.
and i lied last time agaiinn cause i never really did it with anyone.
sorry eugene!!

hi guys i'm at eugene's house and i'm lying cause i'm not bummed i'm all hyper but chill at the same time i guess.  he yelled at my yesterday because i smoke too much weed or something? so giess that bummed me out a little. so now he invited me over and all i want to do is read some books i got from the library but he keeps kissing my neck so thats distracting, so im pretending i have important emails to attend to or something like that.
i havent felt this silly in a long time
i'm gonna go do IT now, byeeeeeeeeeee.

really long, thanks to anyone who reads this. wow. i've been so busy lately, i haven't had time to make a proper update. last week i went to to prom with jake. it was pretty good. not as great as last year, but that was to be expected. nobody can top eugene. monday,tuesday, wednesday: last days of work. finally. i'm too lazy to have a job. at first it was kind of fun, but i started hating having to be there. i didn't like having to schedule things around it. it was impossible to be spontaneous during the week anymore. all i could do was come home, walk perry, then go to work. anyway, friday i went to cody's prom which was okay. everyone was nice enough, but i didn't know any of them. i came home right after it was over. eh, i just wasn't feeling it. got my progress report, and it's not so good. my mom doesn't seem to care, but i'm really disappointed in myself. it's a good thing i dont have work anymore, i cans spend more time studying now and less time hanging out. that's all i've been doing really. saturday i went to see justin for a little, then hung out with eugene and he got of his tatoo finished. i fell asleep at his house and didn't get home til 4 oclock this morning. ugh yesterday i thought perry ran away and i wa SO scared. one of the worst things that has ever happened to me. i guess that's all for now.

<center>i love eugene michael demaio so much.
that's all i have to say
♥♥♥♥♥

i have no time for anything this week.
good stuff:
-prom tomorrow!
-next week is my last week of work
-i'm not going to school tomorrow

feels so good to be home today.  i called in sick to work today :/  whatever.  i woke up really late and played with my puppy all day.  i can't wait to go swimming in my pool.
and i forget what else i wanted to write, so maybe i'll edit this later.

i just got back from work and i am so tired.  this felt like the longest day everrrr.  i'm so tired right now. ugh.  and i'm quitting.  not cause i hate it, but i'm just too lazy to have a job.  and i don't really need it either.  i'd rather spend my time doing other stuff, then being stuck behind a register or cleaning tables. blah.  i played tennis monday and i'm getting better.  so if anyone wants to play doubles i'm up for it.
that's it.

this morning was so overcast and gross out and now i look out my window and the sun is shining and everything looks so green. i love that. i'm going to have to take perry out and enjoy at least some of the day. anything but doing this project for english. i went to church today then out with brad for a little while. i wish i could be more like him. he is such a good person, virtuous is the that comes to mind when i think about him. anyway, i was doing a lot of thinking last night and this morning and i realized i don't have any real friends left. christina and i have grown so far apart. we barely even talk anymore. hanging out with her more like a chore on a to-do list, then just having fun with a friend. it's like trying to throw water out of a sinking ship. sabin isn't talking to me because i'm back together with eugene which i don't understand at all. my relationship with him has nothing to do with her and she really doesn't know him, so who is she to judge. everyone else is basically just an aquaintance. brett and justin... i don't really know them even though we hang out a lot. they're nice people, just not ones i'd call my close friends. so i really feel so lonely. and even counting all of those people, none of them go to my school. i have very few people i can talk to there, and the ones that i do talk to are again not people i would consider close friends. really sucks when you can't talk to anyone because you can't trust them. and that goes out to three specific people. because i made the mistake of trusting them with really private information and they couldn't keep it to themselves.

don't read this if you're going to complain about what i write.k everyone who has so much to say about me needs to stop. none of you people know anything about the person i am. i'm not a whore or a slut. i'm in a monogamous relationship with someone i love alot. i don't cheat on him and i never have. i don't understand why people who don't even know me want to hurt me. i wish it didn't bother me so much, but it does and i'm getting sick and tired of it. thank god there's only 2 more months of school. I can't wait to get out of that place and spend every day with eugene. he's going to england at the end of june and i'm going to miss him soso much. he's so lucky. i wishi could go, but there's no way my mom would ever say yes to that. so far this weekend has been boring. yesterday i went with justin, olivia, and danny to justin's little sister's play, it was really cute, they did annie. after eugene picked me up and we just hung out and he spent the night cause mom and bill are away for the weekend...again. now i supposed to be doing my english project and i haven't accomplished anything at all. i tried to start around 1 and i've done nothing but play on the computer, play with perry, and watch tv. that's it.

<center>"Eventually we're going to live in a society where there will be no secrets.  Where there will be no shame...Whatever it is you are, that will be OK.  Because the rest of the world will understand that everybody has something- and that nothing is ever as it appears."</center>
                                                --Oprah

my mood has really improved since monday. it's hard for me to talk about my depression, so writing it on here is a really big step for me. monday was possibly the worst day i've ever had. i called my mom to have her pick me up and bring me up, but she said everything that was happening was all my fault and i had to stay at school the rest of the day, she would only bring me my medicine. i stopped taking it for about a month, and it's supposed to take awhile, but i feel a little bit better already. calmer i guess. my mom wants me to start going to therapy again, but i'm not sure if i want to. this is all so frustrating for me. this is all i'm going to write for today.

unfortunately i'm taking my medicine medicine again so i feel ok.  i just wish i could be normal and not need medication to feel happy.  i had thrown it out so long ago and i thought i could do without it, but the past couple weeks have just gotten worse and worse.  i don't think i've ever felt that bad ever.  but thank god that's all over now.
th week ended okay despite everything that was going on.  somedays i hate eugene so much, but i was still happy to see him friday.  we got dinner with alex and then he went home.  today i hung out with craig, justin, and brett, played some tennis, which i suck at, saw eugene for about 30 minutes and played some scrabble which i don't suck at.  so far things are looking up and i love you so much!

today kind of sucked
and i haven't done any of my homework yet, so i can't go into detail.
i won't be able to tomorrow either, or tuesday, or wednesday, or thursday.
maybe friday, i'm busy, but not the good kind of busy.

i'm not quite sure why i'm awake so early, but oh well.
this weekend was really nice.  friday we had no school because of teachers' meetings.  i played with perry for most of the day, then went to a party with justin and brett.  i got sick, but eugene took care of meJ. saturday, i was with euegen for awhile, then i went to this volunteer thing i had to do with mentally disabled kids.  it actually turned out to be a lot of fun.  i'm going back this saturday.  sunday just church and went to the park with brad.  the weather has been perfect, i hope it actually stays like this for a long time.  eugene was a creep and left al these notes all over my car, but he ended up surprising me yesterday, so we got to see each other for a little bit, so in the end we basically spent the whole weekend together.  now that it's all typed up, it doesn't seem like i did that much.

hi, i don't know if anyone reads this, actually i know that no one does, but i'm still going to keep writing.  anyways.  life has been really good lately.  i've been very happy.  i feel like i'm burting with happiness.  so let's try and remember all the good stuff that's been going on...friday, i skipped school with jake so i could find a dress for prom.  i found a few potential ones, but i haven't made a definite choice yet, i still need to do some more shopping.  after that we just hung out at his house then picked up greg and tim and hung out with them.  saturday, i think this was the best day of the week.  i picked up christina and we brought perry to tthe park to play.  he is the cutest doggy everever.  after we were  there for awhile, i brought her home and then did some errands for my mom, then justin called to do stuff, so i dropped perry off at home and met up with him and margo.  then later brett came over and we just blazed and watched bad news bears? i dont know what it was called it was funny i think.  and those boys are so silly.  and i always have a lot of fun with them.  then my mom yelled at me cause i didnt get home til 2am i think it was...  then today i went to church and after hung out with brad as usual.
now i am home because it is raining and gross out and it's supposed to snow.  it looks like night time outside.
and im going to go play with perry.bye

i'm not sure what to write in here.  i've been really b usy, but i never feel like talking about anything, but here you go...
monday; nothing at all. i just went to school and then work cause i didn't work yesterday.  tuesday was the same exact thing.  after work i hung out with margo and brett and some other guys.  that was fun.  wednesday; eugene had a show so i went to that.  he and eric just did covers last night, but they were really good.  the show was over like 12, so we got breakfast?
my boyfriend is so sexy and i love him sosoosososoos much. and im really happy right now, but so tired
so
bye

the snow is getting ridiculous.  i'm really sick of it now.  we're not even getting snow days anymore.  i want school to be over so badly.  i can't wait for spring break, i need a vacation from everything.  i've felt so tired this whole week.  all i've really done is go to school and work.  today i went to school and it was snowing again, i was really hoping we'd get out early, but nothing..  after i came home for a little while and played with perry.  then i left to see eric and nick.  there were other things going on tonight, but i just didn't have any energy to go to a party.  i think i prefer just quiet nights,  the whole partying thing is really getting old.  i don't like the way i feel the next day.
